00:11:29,455 --> 00:11:31,355
Nemam komentar trenutno, Ron.

217
00:11:31,390 --> 00:11:33,255
Zasto je Gor predao?

218
00:11:33,292 --> 00:11:35,783
Sacekaj sekund.

219
00:11:35,828 --> 00:11:37,625
Zasto je Gor predao?

220
00:11:37,663 --> 00:11:39,528
Zato sto smo izgubili izbore, Ron.

221
00:12:05,091 --> 00:12:07,787
Jeremi, daj mi Ncka Baldika.

222
00:12:07,827 --> 00:12:10,318
Pozuri.

223
00:12:10,362 --> 00:12:12,227
Ron, Udruzenje novinara

224
00:12:12,264 --> 00:12:14,459
ima drugacije brojke
nego TV mreze.

225
00:12:14,500 --> 00:12:16,661
O cemu ti pricas?
Sve su stanice objavile.

226
00:12:16,702 --> 00:12:18,670
Gor je predao. On je na putu za trg sada...

227
00:12:18,704 --> 00:12:21,673
Slusaj, sve sto ja kazem je, da najstarija
oragnizacija vesti u zemlji,

228
00:12:21,707 --> 00:12:23,607
nije jos objavila rezultate izbora.

229
00:12:23,642 --> 00:12:25,735
Jos uvek verujemo da su Floridini
poranili.

230
00:12:25,778 --> 00:12:28,110
Ja ne razumem
sta vi momci dodjavola radite.

231
00:12:28,147 --> 00:12:30,172
- Sta je to?
- Zvacu te nazad, Ron.

232
00:12:32,017 --> 00:12:34,076
Dobili ste Bila Daleja.
Molim vas ostavite poruku.

233
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:36,918
Dodjavola.

234
00:12:39,558 --> 00:12:40,684
Da, Ron Klajn.

235
00:12:40,726 --> 00:12:43,058
Ron, mislim da mreze
imaju pogresne cifre.

236
00:12:43,095 --> 00:12:45,063
Zvucace ludo...
Sad sam zavrsio sa Baldikom...

237
00:12:45,097 --> 00:12:46,758
masina u Volusiji je poludela.

238
00:12:46,799 --> 00:12:50,200
Pazi ovo... dodala je
sve u svemu 3,000 glasova Busu

239
00:12:50,236 --> 00:12:52,636
i oduzela 1,000 glasova od Gora.

240
00:12:52,671 --> 00:12:54,696
Otisli su unazad.
Gorovi se sad broje

241
00:12:54,740 --> 00:12:57,072
i fali 16,000 u toj oblasti.

242
00:12:57,109 --> 00:12:58,576
Pa koji su pravi brojevi?

243
00:12:58,611 --> 00:13:01,944
Kada preracunas
celu drzavu,

244
00:13:01,981 --> 00:13:04,211
ispod smo za manje od 15,000.

245
00:13:04,250 --> 00:13:06,081
Znaci to je ispravka masine.

246
00:13:06,118 --> 00:13:08,052
- Jos uvek smo zivi.
- Cekaj, ne.

247
00:13:08,087 --> 00:13:10,521
Gor je predao Busu.
On je na putu ka trgu.

248
00:13:10,556 --> 00:13:12,217
Zezas me jel tako?

249
00:13:12,258 --> 00:13:14,488
Zar nisi video vesti?
Sve mreze su objavile.

250
00:13:14,527 --> 00:13:16,961
Isuse. Sacekaj.

251
00:13:16,996 --> 00:13:19,328
Ljudi, sta se dogadja?
Sta se dogadja?

252
00:13:19,365 --> 00:13:21,890
CNN je obavesten od dva starija
zvanicnika Gorove kampanje

253
00:13:21,934 --> 00:13:24,994
da je podprecednik uputio poziv
guverneru Teksasa.

254
00:13:25,037 --> 00:13:28,006
Podprecednik sada na svojoj paradi ovde u
donjem gradu Nesvila

255
00:13:28,040 --> 00:13:30,668
na samo nekoliko minuta od
davanja komentara svojim glasacima...

256
00:13:30,709 --> 00:13:33,769
isuse Hriste. Zovi mi Bila Daleja.

257
00:13:33,813 --> 00:13:36,407
Ne ne, nemogu ga dobiti.
Pokusavao sam. Ne mogu nikog da dobijem.

258
00:13:36,448 --> 00:13:38,109
Sta se ovde dodjavola dogadja?

259
00:13:38,150 --> 00:13:40,641
Cekaj, Dalej... mozes ga dobiti
preko signala iz kancelarije Bele Kuce.

260
00:13:40,686 --> 00:13:43,314
- Pokusaj to.
- Da, da.

261
00:13:43,355 --> 00:13:45,050
Nema glasa
o Gorovoj kampanji jos uvek.

262
00:13:45,090 --> 00:13:47,149
Pokusali smo da napravimo
neke pozive...

263
00:13:48,260 --> 00:13:50,023
Sranje.

264
00:13:56,535 --> 00:13:58,628
- Dobili ste Dona Brazila...
- Prokletstvo.

265
00:13:58,671 --> 00:14:01,037
- Pokusaj Lihejna, on je mogao vec stici.
- Dobra ideja.

266
00:14:01,073 --> 00:14:03,940
Ne, on nije u ovoj knjizi.
On je u ovoj.

267
00:14:03,976 --> 00:14:07,207
Mreze su pogresile
dva puta u jednoj noci?

268
00:14:07,246 --> 00:14:08,770
Idemo na ponovno
prebrojavanje masine.

269
00:14:08,814 --> 00:14:10,679
Moramo da stignemo
do njega pre nego sto se pone na binu.

270
00:14:10,716 --> 00:14:12,809
Sta god da se desi, nesmeo dozvoliti
da odrzi taj govor.

271
00:14:12,852 --> 00:14:14,615
- Ko ce ga zgrabiti?
- Morhaus.

272
00:14:14,653 --> 00:14:16,086
Presrescemo ga kolima.

273
00:14:16,121 --> 00:14:17,850
Daj mi Dejvida Morhausa.

274
00:14:17,890 --> 00:14:20,950
Cucemo podprecednika,
receno nam je, za oko petnaest minuta.

275
00:14:25,097 --> 00:14:26,655
Morhaus ovde.

276
00:14:26,699 --> 00:14:29,293
Gor nije izgubio.
Moras da ga zaustavis kod kola.

277
00:14:29,335 --> 00:14:32,099
Kola podprecednika Al gora
su stigla.

278
00:14:32,137 --> 00:14:34,833
Gosp. Gor ce verovatno
dati vrlo kratku izjavu.

279
00:14:34,874 --> 00:14:38,207
Hocemo Gora!
Hocemo Gora !

280
00:14:52,625 --> 00:14:55,253
Ne ne ne,
Gosp. Podprecednice,

281
00:14:55,294 --> 00:14:57,125
Gosp. Podprecednice.

282
00:14:57,162 --> 00:14:58,993
Sir, Gosp. Podprecednice.

283
00:15:05,070 --> 00:15:07,197
Whoa whoa whoa.
Sacekaj sekund. Cekaj, drugar.

284
00:15:07,239 --> 00:15:08,934
Znamo da je podprecednik
iza scene.

285
00:15:08,974 --> 00:15:11,772
Pokusavali smo da saznamo vise
od njegovih starijih pomagaca

286
00:15:11,810 --> 00:15:13,505
o razlozimna odlaganja.

287
00:15:13,545 --> 00:15:15,206
Ali nismo bili uspesni u tome...

288
00:15:15,247 --> 00:15:18,842
Moji ljudi ne vide iste cifre
kao TV mreze.

289
00:15:18,884 --> 00:15:20,875
Ni Karl.

290
00:15:23,489 --> 00:15:25,480
Hocemo Gora!
Hocemo Gora!

291
00:15:28,327 --> 00:15:30,625
Gosp. Podprecednice.

292
00:15:30,663 --> 00:15:32,563
Gosp. Podprecednice.

293
00:15:32,598 --> 00:15:34,225
Sir, sir.

294
00:15:34,266 --> 00:15:35,893
- Sir,hitno je.
- Sta je Dejvide?

295
00:15:35,935 --> 00:15:38,369
Dalej mora da razgovara sa vama.
Treba mu samo pet minuta.

296
00:15:38,404 --> 00:15:40,031
Upravo sam razgovarao sa Busom.
Ceka me

297
00:15:40,072 --> 00:15:42,097
odrzim govor.
Necu da ga pustim da ceka.

298
00:15:42,141 --> 00:15:43,802
Molim Vas, molim Vas, molim Vas
Gosp. Podprecednice,

299
00:15:43,842 --> 00:15:47,573
postoji problem sa prebrojavanjem na Floridi.

300
00:15:47,613 --> 00:15:50,138
....glas popularnosti koji izgleda
kao najblizi...

301
00:15:50,182 --> 00:15:52,582
Guverneru Al Gor je na vezi.

302
00:15:54,620 --> 00:15:56,918
Da vidim da sam dobro razumeo.

303
00:15:56,956 --> 00:16:00,153
Zvali ste da povucete svoju predaju?

304
00:16:00,192 --> 00:16:04,652
Izvinite, ali ne morate da se ljutite zbog toga.

305
00:16:04,697 --> 00:16:07,962
Moj mali brat me uverava
da sam pobedio na Floridi.

306
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:11,401
Pa, vas mali brat nije
najveci autoritet po ovom pitanju.

307
00:16:11,437 --> 00:16:14,201
Gosp. Podprecednice,
uradite sta morate.

308
00:16:17,576 --> 00:16:19,635
Da!

309
00:16:22,181 --> 00:16:24,240
Podprecednik je ponovo zvao guvernera

310
00:16:24,283 --> 00:16:26,547
i povukao predaju.

311
00:16:26,585 --> 00:16:29,110
Ovo ce biti gotovo za najvise
24, 48 sati.

312
00:16:29,154 --> 00:16:31,952
- Dragi...
- Da?

313
00:16:31,991 --> 00:16:34,687
Budi oprezan tamo dole.
Imaju aligatore.

314
00:16:34,727 --> 00:16:36,524
Vidimo se u petak.

315
00:16:36,562 --> 00:16:39,588
Gosp. Podprecednik
je pozvao guvernera Busa

316
00:16:39,631 --> 00:16:41,690
da povuce predaju.

317
00:16:41,734 --> 00:16:45,101
Sta vicu ovi ljudi?
Daj da slusamo, pojacaj zvuk.

318
00:16:45,137 --> 00:16:46,764
Ponovno brojanje!

319
00:16:46,805 --> 00:16:49,205
"Ponovno brojanje. "
Kazu, "Ponovno brojanje. "

320
00:17:06,291 --> 00:17:09,454
Sekretar drzave
Katarina Haris govori.

321
00:17:09,495 --> 00:17:11,554
Sta se dodjavola dogadja Katarina?

322
00:17:11,597 --> 00:17:13,360
Koje su konacne cifre?

323
00:17:13,399 --> 00:17:15,959
Ovde je sekretar drzave Katarina Haris.

324
00:17:16,001 --> 00:17:18,367
Moramo zvati Kleja Robertsa,
Direktora...

325
00:17:18,404 --> 00:17:20,872
Katarina, Dzeb je!
Koji su konacni brojevi?

326
00:17:20,906 --> 00:17:23,170
Ko je pobedio na Floridi?

327
00:17:23,208 --> 00:17:25,938
Evo je!
Sekretarko Haris.

328
00:17:40,359 --> 00:17:42,520
Dacemo izjavu kasnije.

329
00:17:42,561 --> 00:17:45,029
Bus je dobio

330
00:17:45,064 --> 00:17:48,727
2,909,135 glasova.

331
00:17:48,767 --> 00:17:50,234
Gor je dobio

332
00:17:50,269 --> 00:17:53,727
2,907,351 glasova.

333
00:17:55,607 --> 00:17:57,939
Kolika je razlika, Klej?

334
00:17:57,976 --> 00:18:00,069
Oh, izvini.

335
00:18:07,052 --> 00:18:10,783
Bus uzima Floridu
za 1,784 glasova.

336
00:18:10,823 --> 00:18:13,257
Ili. 03%.

337
00:18:13,292 --> 00:18:16,489
Bilo kaoja razlika manja od. 5 do 1%

338
00:18:16,528 --> 00:18:20,294
okida drugi krug za mandat.

339
00:18:21,934 --> 00:18:24,334
Hvala Klej.

340
00:18:29,975 --> 00:18:31,670
Sada cemo nastaviti

341
00:18:31,710 --> 00:18:34,577
na drugi krug mandata.

342
00:18:34,613 --> 00:18:36,843
Sve sto je bilo potrebno je 30,000

343
00:18:36,882 --> 00:18:38,850
da se pokrene automatsko drugi krug glasanja.

344
00:18:38,884 --> 00:18:41,785
Iza smo za samo 1,784.

345
00:18:41,820 --> 00:18:43,788
Pusti ce svaki listic

346
00:18:43,822 --> 00:18:45,653
kroz masinu za merenje ponovo.

347
00:18:45,691 --> 00:18:47,318
Masine nisu precizne.

348
00:18:47,359 --> 00:18:49,350
Dobicete malo drugaciji ukupan zbir

349
00:18:49,394 --> 00:18:51,362
svaki put kad ih propustite kroz masinu.

350
00:18:51,396 --> 00:18:53,864
Moguce je cak da cemo voditi do sutra ujutru.

351
00:18:53,899 --> 00:18:55,560
Ali ako Bus nastavi da vodi,

352
00:18:55,601 --> 00:18:58,229
Siguran sam da ce hteti da brzo deluju

353
00:18:58,270 --> 00:18:59,965
i Katarina Haris ce pokusati
da opravda

354
00:19:00,005 --> 00:19:01,836
Busovu pobedu sve do isteka roka,

355
00:19:01,874 --> 00:19:04,536
- sto je za sest dana.
- Naravno da hoce.

356
00:19:04,576 --> 00:19:06,510
Ona je saradnik na katedri za njegovu
kampanju na Floridi.

357
00:19:06,545 --> 00:19:08,479
Ona bi mu odobrila jos pre nekoliko meseci
da je mogla.

358
00:19:08,514 --> 00:19:11,039
Da li je neko ovde cuo za"cad"?

359
00:19:14,887 --> 00:19:17,788
Jedna po jedna, svaka od 67
drzava Floride

360
00:19:17,823 --> 00:19:20,690
su ponovo propustile
svoje glasacke listice kroz masine.

361
00:19:20,726 --> 00:19:23,194
Ovaj proces su nadgledale tri osobe
iz odbora za prebrojavanje glasova

362
00:19:24,229 --> 00:19:25,958
sacinjne od drzavnih
i lokalnih zvanicnika.

363
00:19:25,998 --> 00:19:29,195
- Konacni total mora biti predat...
- Da, sta je, Dzo?

364
00:19:29,234 --> 00:19:31,600
Jel gledas?
Dalej je na kanalu 6.

365
00:19:33,372 --> 00:19:35,237
Mr. Dalej, zasto mislite

366
00:19:35,274 --> 00:19:36,639
da ce rezultati drugog kruga

367
00:19:36,675 --> 00:19:38,666
biti drugaciji nego sada?

368
00:19:38,710 --> 00:19:40,701
Pa, ovog trenutka niko ne zna, Met,

369
00:19:40,746 --> 00:19:42,373
da li ce biti drugaciji ili ne.

370
00:19:42,414 --> 00:19:44,780
Njegov tata je ukrao od JFK,

371
00:19:44,816 --> 00:19:46,545
a sad ce on da ukrade od Gora.

372
00:19:46,585 --> 00:19:49,554
Pitao sam Vorena Kristofera,
bivseg sekretara drzave,

373
00:19:49,588 --> 00:19:51,647
da dodje i nadgleda prebrojavanje za nas...

374
00:19:51,690 --> 00:19:54,181
- Ok, timaju Vorena Kristofera Warren Christopher.
.... Sekretara drzave

375
00:19:54,226 --> 00:19:56,251
Voren Kristofer
ce voditi Gorov pravni tim...

376
00:19:56,295 --> 00:19:58,286
Koga mi mislimo?

377
00:19:59,731 --> 00:20:02,291
Oh, to ce biti nocna mora.

378
00:20:02,334 --> 00:20:04,393
Svaki advokat
od Nju Jorka do Havane

379
00:20:04,436 --> 00:20:07,837
ce mahati svojim aktovkama
gore dole ulicama Floride.

380
00:20:07,873 --> 00:20:09,340
Kazem vam,

381
00:20:09,374 --> 00:20:12,309
padace sa neba.

382
00:20:12,344 --> 00:20:15,211
- Mozes li da se vratis na aerodrom?
- Bicu tamo za sat vremena.

383
00:20:18,750 --> 00:20:21,947
Stotine glasaca su dosli danas
u oblast palm Bica

384
00:20:21,987 --> 00:20:25,650
da potpisu izjavu kojom potvrdjuju
da su bili zbunjeni izbornim listicima.

385
00:20:25,691 --> 00:20:28,626
Peticija kruzi zahtevajuci ponovno glasanje.

386
00:20:28,660 --> 00:20:30,855
Glasaci veruju da su pogresno glasali

387
00:20:30,896 --> 00:20:33,956
-za Pat Buchanan...
- Hocu da se moj glas racuna.

388
00:20:33,999 --> 00:20:35,899
Ucinicemo sve da osiguramo

389
00:20:35,934 --> 00:20:37,834
da su vasi glasovi prebrojani.
Zato smo ovde.

390
00:20:37,869 --> 00:20:39,769
Osecam se kao zaglavljen

391
00:20:39,805 --> 00:20:41,670
u "Nocima zivih Bubija. "

392
00:20:41,707 --> 00:20:43,675
Samo ostani miran
I sta god da radis,

393
00:20:43,709 --> 00:20:46,269
- nemoj vikati "Pogodak!"
- Da, obecavam.

394
00:20:46,311 --> 00:20:48,802
Hej, Buchanan je na TV.
Zvacu te ponovo.

395
00:20:48,847 --> 00:20:51,714
....Ja mislim i verujem.
I moje je verovanje

396
00:20:51,750 --> 00:20:54,184
da su neki od glasaca
koji su birali mene

397
00:20:54,219 --> 00:20:56,278
verovatno glasali za mene greskom

398
00:20:56,321 --> 00:20:59,848
uvereni da daju svoj glas Al Goru.

399
00:20:59,891 --> 00:21:02,382
Glen, nova polazna tacka...

400
00:21:02,427 --> 00:21:04,895
Buchanan je upravobio na TV.
Cak i on kaze da misli

401
00:21:04,930 --> 00:21:06,955
da su ljudi glasali za njega misleci da glasaju za Gora.

402
00:21:06,999 --> 00:21:08,660
Zapisi.
Posalji mi na mail.

403
00:21:08,700 --> 00:21:10,827
Precasni Dzesi Dzekson
vodi mars demokrata

404
00:21:10,869 --> 00:21:14,361
i nezadovoljnih glasaca
kroz West Palm Beach.

405
00:21:14,406 --> 00:21:17,204
U ovom momentu ne znamo

406
00:21:17,242 --> 00:21:19,574
ko je pobedio na izborima

407
00:21:19,611 --> 00:21:23,172
jer nasi glasovi
jos nisu prebrojani ponovo.

408
00:21:23,215 --> 00:21:25,445
Tako je.

409
00:21:32,824 --> 00:21:34,655
To je suludo.

410
00:21:34,693 --> 00:21:38,356
Posle izbora, sada sve oci na Floridi
gledaju drugi krug.

411
00:21:38,397 --> 00:21:40,058
Tim od oko 70 ljudi

412
00:21:40,098 --> 00:21:42,794
se ocekuju u drzavi
u narednih 24 casa,

413
00:21:42,834 --> 00:21:45,268
trebali bi da naglasimo,
mnogi su potegli pitanja

414
00:21:45,304 --> 00:21:48,501
da li ce Gorova kampanja
pokleknuti...

415
00:22:09,594 --> 00:22:12,461
....od manjka i viska glasova
na nivou obezbedjenja...

416
00:22:15,500 --> 00:22:18,901
Uh, dobar dan,
Gospodine sekretare.

417
00:22:21,306 --> 00:22:24,070
Ovo su svi...
pet advokata i Joe Allbaugh?

418
00:22:25,977 --> 00:22:28,207
Kazi Ostinu, hocu operativce,
PR i volontere

419
00:22:28,246 --> 00:22:31,215
- ovamo smesta.
- Vazi.

420
00:22:31,249 --> 00:22:33,911
Imaju Dzesija Dzeksona
ovde u Palm Bicu

421
00:22:33,952 --> 00:22:36,045
drzi se za ruke sa nekim
od tih starijih jevreja

422
00:22:36,088 --> 00:22:38,147
vristi,
"Prebrojte sve glasove!"

423
00:22:38,190 --> 00:22:39,919
Ko ce se dodjavola prepirati sa tim?

424
00:22:39,958 --> 00:22:42,256
Predpostavljam da ce Gospodin Dzekson

425
00:22:42,294 --> 00:22:44,558
zadrzati njegove "Hymietown" komentare na minimumu

426
00:22:44,596 --> 00:22:46,564
ovoga puta.

427
00:22:46,598 --> 00:22:49,499
Hocu nase protestante
ovde u Palm Bicu,

428
00:22:49,534 --> 00:22:51,729
Talahasi i Majami...
zovi Rodzera Stona...

429
00:22:51,770 --> 00:22:54,398
Ft. Lauderdale, Tampa.

430
00:22:54,439 --> 00:22:56,600
Karl protestante ispred Gorove kuce.

431
00:22:56,641 --> 00:22:59,576
Eto ti.
Sad, slusajte narode,

432
00:22:59,611 --> 00:23:02,580
ovo je ulicna borba
